Class GuavaSpanStoreAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • zipkin.spanstore.guava.GuavaSpanStoreAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GuavaAsyncSpanConsumer, GuavaSpanStore

    public final class GuavaSpanStoreAdapter
extends Object
implements GuavaSpanStore
    A GuavaSpanStore derived from an AsyncSpanStore and an AsyncSpanConsumer. Used by callers who prefer to compose futures.
